WEBVTT

00:02.020 --> 00:03.100
- Ever think it might be a lie?

00:03.100 --> 00:05.420
- I'm thinking that in five years,
this is all gone!

00:05.420 --> 00:08.980
No-one is ever going to sing your
favourite song, ever again.

00:08.980 --> 00:12.020
- You can't break the vow of the
confessional, can you?

00:12.020 --> 00:13.580
I hurt someone.

00:13.580 --> 00:15.020
That's my confession.

00:15.020 --> 00:17.500
- All right, so why this bloke? I
mean, why this priest?

00:17.500 --> 00:18.780
It can't just be random.

00:18.780 --> 00:20.220
- Can somebody help me?

00:20.220 --> 00:22.140
- You see, this killer, he's on a
spree.

00:22.140 --> 00:23.980
Unless you give us a name,

00:23.980 --> 00:25.900
more people are going to die.

00:25.900 --> 00:27.380
- I'm sorry.

00:27.380 --> 00:28.580
I can't help you.

00:28.580 --> 00:30.140
- Did my dad rape you?!

00:30.140 --> 00:31.980
- Yes.

00:31.980 --> 00:33.060
- We cut you a deal.

00:33.060 --> 00:36.500
We keep your son out of prison, you
bring us Charlie Hicks.

00:36.500 --> 00:38.700
- If you can find out what she's
done with this file,

00:38.700 --> 00:41.420
then she's not in your life any
more.

00:41.420 --> 00:43.540
- ...some praying...
- The Hard Sun is coming,

00:43.540 --> 00:45.700
and I am its messenger.

00:45.700 --> 00:46.940
If he's there...

00:49.460 --> 00:50.740
...let him stop me.

